Newly-opened MRT station in a somewhat isolated location. The exits on the eastern side of the station currently serve dead-end roads to nowhere
As this is the current terminal station, use Exit 3 if you want to transfer to or from onward buses. Exit 2 serves condos in the vicinity of the station.

The new Thomson–East Coast line station opened on June 23, 2024. This is a temporary terminal station as it is still under construction.
